{"tid":1754252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭生實用救港提議，身在台灣心在港","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:00:15.000Z","uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28a22979e667f8710936cea4d2d93b24ec477865","tid":1754252,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"所有泛民同我入嚟<br />\n你地記住，係我地推你上去<br />\n今次係香港人贏左其中一仗，唔淨係多一個議席，更加要<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>持續光復18區光復香港</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下事情必須做</span></span>：<br />\n1. 用盡可用嘅資源，<span style=\"color: gold;\">救走＆支援</span>所有有需要嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n2. 18區區議會<span style=\"color: gold;\">必須改革</span>，所有議會記錄必須公開，開放更多民眾資詢方法<br />\n<br />\n3. 令議會<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔可以再成為財團搖錢樹</span>，地區工程費用必須受到監測<br />\n<br />\n4. 幫助自己區改善法團，<span style=\"color: gold;\">監測管理公司＋屋苑財政</span><br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">成立「18區聯合區議會」，建立一個資詢平台</span></span><br />\n         <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 不理黃藍</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">代表香港人同港共中共談判所有事情</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LI9FgLyyDhM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLI9FgLyyDhM&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=12bd6c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LI9FgLyyDhM</a>"},{"pid":"329e59a1c07533bf3fe3e4de75e01e6ff1e05073","tid":1754252,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"救港自推＋1"},{"pid":"fe22104dae150c35733b273917eba91a574d76dd","tid":1754252,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"救港自推＋2"},{"pid":"4a1cf63aaee5f680ca95109736473a667b3f7502","tid":1754252,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB